WEBVTT

00:00:29.392 --> 00:00:32.417
Stvari koje vi i ja možda vidimo

00:00:32.417 --> 00:00:34.532
kao globalne probleme,

00:00:34.532 --> 00:00:37.180
poput klimatskih promena, energetske krize

00:00:37.180 --> 00:00:38.842
ili siromaštva,

00:00:38.842 --> 00:00:43.702
su u mnogim slučajevima gradski problemi.

00:00:43.702 --> 00:00:45.564
Neće biti rešeni

00:00:45.564 --> 00:00:48.582
dok ljudi koji žive u gradovima,

00:00:48.582 --> 00:00:50.501
poput većine nas,

00:00:50.501 --> 00:00:53.293
zapravo ne počnu da rade bolje,

00:00:53.293 --> 00:00:57.249
jer upravo sada,
ne obavljamo dobar posao.

00:00:57.249 --> 00:01:00.585
To postaje prilično jasno